
If you have a single other system connected using firewire and
just want to get the logs from there use as root

modprobe raw1394
firescope -Aut System.map

If you want a log file add -wLOGFILE

System.map is the System.map from the target system

(or firescope32 .. if it's a 32bit target)

For more information, see:
ftp://ftp.suse.de/private/bk/firewire/docs/debugging-via-ohci1394.txt
